)"},{"index":1,"text":"如果你愿意点开某部雌小鬼本子的评论区，你会发现一个有趣的现象： 大家几乎很少讨论女主，讨论焦点一般集中在剧情上。 这种现象其实很反常，因为大部分人来某些app找本子看时，同时也是迫切需要解决生理需求时， 在这种情况下，大家其实是没什么精力来仔细看剧情的，都是把前期剧情稍微看个大概，然后直接快进到正戏。 事后大家也都忙着打扫卫生去了，更没空去看剧情。 而我个人一直有一个观点： 存在即合理，如果一个现象不仅…","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/content","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 709, 187)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 1017 - 753, 1204)"}]},{"index":6,"resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/vote_btn","class":"android.widget.ImageView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 66, 66)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 1248 - 110, 1314)"},{"index":7,"text":"7613","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/vote_count","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 144, 66)","boundsInScreen":"(110, 1248 - 254, 1314)"},{"index":8,"resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/comment_btn","class":"android.widget.ImageView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 66, 66)","boundsInScreen":"(254, 1248 - 320, 1314)"},{"index":9,"text":"493","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/comment_count","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"e